data.description: ALL INVESTORS STOP HERE!!!!  This great home on the lake comes with its own tenant. What a great opportunity!! This lake home offers beautiful views of North Lake. You can play in the water or fish from your very own private dock!  One story with three bedrooms and two baths, the kitchen opens to the living room and there are views of the lake from both rooms.  The view from the dining room will take your breath away!  The primary bedroom is spacious with its own bathroom.  The primary bathroom has a large walk in shower and separate toilet area.    Silver Lakes is a private community located between Barstow and Victorville.  The amenities include a 27 hole championship golf course, bocce ball courts, tennis courts, pickle ball courts, a community swimming pool, gym, equestrian area and two gorgeous lakes for fishing, boating, kayaking, and paddle boarding.
